    Id         = 'QUORUM-WITNESS-LOSS'
    Explain    = 'Quorum was lost (Event 1177 / node removed 1135, cluster.log quorum-arbitration entries, or a non-normal quorum state in the HA DMVs). When the cluster cannot maintain quorum it shuts the cluster service down and the SQL role goes offline.'
